The next() method of the Iterator interface returns an Object, which is not the same as the Staff class.
To fix this, you can cast the Object returned by next() to a Staff object, like this:
Staff staffMember = (Staff) it.next();

This will ensure that the Object returned by next() is cast to a Staff object, which will allow you to use the Staff class methods on it.
